# Settings - <%= @ai_agent.display_name %>

<% if @ai_agent.archived? && @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
**Status: Inactive** — This agent is deactivated and not being billed.

<% if !@current_user.billing_exempt? %>
<% if @proration_amount_cents %>
Reactivating this agent will charge **$<%= "%.2f" % (@proration_amount_cents / 100.0) %> now** (prorated), then **$3/month** thereafter.
<% else %>
Reactivating this agent will add **$3/month** to your subscription, prorated for the current billing period.
<% end %>
<% end %>

To reactivate, visit this page in your browser and use the reactivation form.

<% else %>
## Profile

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Name | <%= @ai_agent.name %> |
| Handle | `<%= @ai_agent.handle %>` |
| Mode | <%= @ai_agent.internal_ai_agent? ? "Internal" : "External" %> |
<% if @ai_agent.internal_ai_agent? %>
| Model | `<%= @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("model") || "default" %>` |
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent.internal_ai_agent? && @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("identity_prompt").present? %>
## Identity Prompt

```
<%= @ai_agent.agent_configuration&.dig("identity_prompt") %>
```
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent_collectives.any? %>
## Collective Memberships

<% @ai_agent_collectives.each do |collective| %>
* [<%= collective.name %>](<%= collective.path %>)
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @available_collectives.any? %>
## Add to Collective

Add this agent (ID: `<%= @ai_agent.id %>`) to one of your collectives:

<% @available_collectives.each do |collective| %>
* [<%= collective.name %>](<%= collective.path %>/settings/actions/add_ai_agent_to_collective) - use `ai_agent_id: <%= @ai_agent.id %>`
<% end %>
<% end %>

## API Tokens

<% if @ai_agent.api_tokens.external.any? %>
| Name | Created | Last Used | Expires | Status |
|------|---------|-----------|---------|--------|
<% @ai_agent.api_tokens.external.each do |token| %>
| <%= token.name || 'Unnamed' %> | <%= time_ago_in_words(token.created_at) %> ago | <%= token.last_used_at ? time_ago_in_words(token.last_used_at) + ' ago' : 'Never' %> | <%= time_ago_in_words(token.expires_at) %> | <%= token.active? ? 'Active' : 'Inactive' %> |
<% end %>
<% else %>
This agent has no API tokens.
<% end %>

<% if @ai_agent.external_ai_agent? %>
* [Create Token](<%= @ai_agent.path %>/settings/tokens/new)
<% else %>
*Internal agents cannot have API tokens.*
<% end %>

<% if @current_tenant.feature_enabled?("stripe_billing") %>
## Deactivate Agent

Deactivating this agent will remove the $3/month charge from your subscription. The agent's data will be preserved and you can reactivate it at any time.

To deactivate, visit this page in your browser.
<% end %>
<% end %>

